                  </hi>. I live in Castle-street, Southwark. On the morning of the 10th of Sept. I was at the foot of London-bridge—a policeman spoke to me, I put my hand down, and missed my handkerchief from my coat-pocket, where it had been safe about five minutes before—this is my handkerchief.</p>
